description: Welcome to this beautifully maintained first-floor condo, perfectly situated in a high-quality, newer construction building in the heart of South Boston. Featuring a thoughtfully designed layout, this bright and airy home offers two generously sized bedrooms and two spa-like bathrooms, complemented by soaring ceilings and rich hardwood floors throughout. The sleek, modern kitchen is outfitted with high-end appliances and opens to a private back patio—ideal for entertaining or relaxing outdoors. Additional highlights include in-unit laundry, central air conditioning, and a spacious 83 sq. ft. private storage room in the basement. Enjoy the unbeatable convenience of being just steps from vibrant West Broadway, where you'll find top-rated restaurants, boutique shops, and easy access to public transportation. This move-in-ready unit is a rare opportunity to enjoy stylish city living in a prime location.
